  <h3 class="group-title" id="about-local-covid-alert-levels">About local COVID alert levels</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The government has introduced a new system called ‘local COVID alert levels’. This will replace current guidance on 14 October. Until then, you must follow the guidance listed under ‘Areas with local restrictions’, below.</p>
</div>
</div>


  <div data-module="track-click">
        <ul class="gem-c-document-list">
