  <h3 class="group-title" id="areas-with-local-restrictions">Areas with local restrictions</h3>
    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>You must follow the local restrictions guidance until 14 October. From this date, you must follow the local COVID alert levels guidance, above.</p>
</div>
</div>


